<time_sig>L.M. (8.8.8.8.)</time_sig>
<title>God's mercies are renewed every day. ƲIT9</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa na̱ pi̱ hullo ka,
 Laua kʋt a biliʋshke;
 Peh onna hosh oyunnakma
 Achakʋt a ma̱ha̱yʋshke.

[V2]
 Onnahinli moyuma ka,
 Et pi̱ hullo fiehnʋshke;
 Onnahinli fichak chito
 Mih mak o̱ chiyuhmi hoke.

[V3]
 Ninak il a foha hi a̱
 Ikbit pihi̱ma tok oke.
 Pi nusikma, achukmʋlit
 Pi apesahanchi hoke.

[V4]
 Nan i̱ nukha̱klo achukma,
 Nan i̱ hullo mʋt bilia;
 Chihowa hʋt achukmʋshke,
 Iloh aiokpahanchashke.

[V5]
 E moma kʋt chitoli hosh,
 Il aiokpʋchi hokbano:
 Chihowa achukma yoke;
 Iloh aiokpahanchashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chihowa na̱ pi̱ hullo ka</aka>
</song>